Acceptance Criteria

GIVEN a return is completed
AND RequestAllowed = true
AND no matching restitution request exists
WHEN backend processing is triggered
THEN a new ServiceNow Request is created

AND the Request is created using the correct offering Sys ID

AND all required variables are sent in the request creation payload

AND the application resolves the ServiceNow Sys ID of:
- the visitor / initiator
- the supplier
- the recipient
- the stockroom
- the returned equipment
before creating the Request

AND the created Request generates an RITM and a ServiceNow task

WHEN the generated task is available
THEN the application updates it through API

AND the task is updated with:
- the comptoir assignment group
- the technician identity
- the expected resolved/completed status


